  schema:name "Jineoloji" ;
  schema:description "The Kurdish women's movement's indigenous feminist theory — 'the science of women' (from Kurmanji jin, 'woman') — arguing that the domination of women is the template for all other domination. Developed within the PKK/KCK framework, practiced in Rojava." ;
